options.content:
TM-SMG

TELEFONIA MOVIL SAMSUNG

targets.rawSQL:
SELECT 
    cod_lprod_19m,
    cod_uorg_pp10,
    cod_planta_pp18,
    oee,
    disponibilidad,
    productividad,
    calidad,
    SUM(producidos) AS producidos,
    SUM(rechazados) AS rechazados,
    MAX(pnp) AS pnp,
    MAX(sum_takt_time) AS sum_takt_time,
    origen,
    hora,
    rn_orden,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
        PARTITION BY cod_lprod_19m
        ORDER BY hora
    ) AS fila,
    COALESCE(sku, 'SKU no informado') AS sku,
    MAX(refreshed) as fecha_act,
    MAX(refreshed) as hora_act
FROM "oee_dashboard"."oee_v_indicadores_calc_unif_multi"
WHERE origen = 'TDF'
  AND cod_planta_pp18 = 'TDF3'
  AND cod_uorg_pp10 = 'TM-SMG'
  AND cod_lprod_19m IN ('TM01','TM02','TM03','TM04','TM05','TM06','TM07','TM08','TM09','TM10')
GROUP BY 
    cod_lprod_19m,
    cod_uorg_pp10,
    cod_planta_pp18,
    oee,
    disponibilidad,
    productividad,
    calidad,
    origen,
    hora,
    rn_orden,
    sku;
